-- Froneman Sees Continued Disruptions at Platinum Mines
-- B y
-- 2012-08-27T11:57:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-27/froneman-sees-continued-disruptions-at-platinum-mines-video-.html
Justin Froneman, an analyst at SBG 
Securities Ltd., discusses the outlook for the mining industry 
after the deaths of 44 people at Lonmin Plc's platinum mine in 
Marikana.  He speaks from Johannesburg with  Guy Johnson  on Bloomberg 
Television's "The Pulse." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 06:06
 